<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>My E-commerce Site</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./stylesheet/index.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./stylesheet/navbar.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("./partials/navbar.ejs") %>

    <section id="hero">
      <h1>Welcome to My E-commerce Site</h1>
      <p>Discover our latest collection of products</p>
      <button>Shop Now</button>
    </section>

    <section id="featured-products">
      <h2>Featured Products</h2>
      <div class="product">
        <img src="./image/echodot.jpg" alt="Product 1" />
        <h3>Amazon Echo Dot</h3>
        <p>
          The Echo Dot is a smart speaker that connects to Amazon's virtual
          assistant, Alexa. It allows you to control your smart home devices,
          play music, ask questions, set alarms, and more, all using your voice.
          The compact design makes it easy to place in any room of your home.
        </p>
        <button>Add to Cart</button>
      </div>
      <div class="product">
        <img src="./image/iphone13.jpg" alt="Product 2" />
        <h3>Apple iPhone 13</h3>
        <p>
          The iPhone 13 is the latest model in Apple's popular smartphone
          lineup. It features a stunning OLED display, an A15 Bionic chip, and
          up to 1TB of storage. It also boasts improved cameras and longer
          battery life, making it a great choice for anyone in the market for a
          new phone.
        </p>
        <button>Add to Cart</button>
      </div>
      <div class="product">
        <img src="./image/nikeair.jpg" alt="Product 3" />
        <h3>Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 38</h3>
        <p>
          The Air Zoom Pegasus 38 is a popular running shoe from Nike. It
          features a breathable mesh upper, responsive cushioning, and a durable
          rubber outsole. It's designed for runners of all levels, and the
          stylish design means it can also be worn for casual everyday use.
        </p>
        <button>Add to Cart</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="newsletter">
      <h2>Subscribe to Our Newsletter</h2>
      <form>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email address" />
        <button>Subscribe</button>
      </form>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2023 My E-commerce Site</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
